aph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >5. Achieve great results to receive more cards for your deck.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >6. Work for various departments, each representing a circle of Hell, and cooperate with them.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >7. Ensure that sinners do not damage our property by keeping them from passing through.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >8. Receive wages for each shift based on the number of sinners punished. Your success depends solely on you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >9. Be an integral part of our fun and delightful team with a shared dark sense of humor.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2181610/extras/afc9d4a9160877ea91579c1a9f3523df.avif?t=1774266764\" width=616 height=180 /></span></p>",
